e reason being is these two used to work together previouslynow all of a sudden they are heading up the digital operations of this european asset manager some might say the old saying could come into play here it’s not what you know it’s who you knowif you make it past the month within this department after having to suffer constant harassment insane decisions poor web practice and having no say or involvement in any web related decisions then you have done amazingly well in fact you deserve an awardin regards to the rest of the company i found other departments to be pretty good there are some very clever and nice people within the organisation and it is run by a very astute man monsieur carmignac unfortunately the company is let down on a digital side by very poor management and a lack of knowledge from senior members of the digital teamadvice to managementtake a good hard look at the digital team there are massive problems there although im sure you already know thisshare on facebookshare on twittershare on whatsappshare via emailcopy linklink copiedflag as inappropriateflag as inappropriatehelpful  carmignac gestion response seconds agoedit • delete carmignac gestion 2  pdtreviews  carmignac gestion there are newer employer reviews for carmignac gestionsee most recent there are newer employer reviews for carmignac gestionsee most recentwork at carmignac gestion share your experiencescarmignac gestionstarvery dissatisfiedstardissatisfiedstarneutral okstarsatisfiedstarvery satisfied  click to ratestart your revieworadd a salaryadd benefitsadd an interviewadd a salaryadd benefitsadd an interviewcloseoutline of two peoples headswork in hr or marketinggrow your employer brandget a free employer accountview allnum of numclose esc job seekers also viewedpnc financial services group reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviewsdeutsche bank reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviewsthe blackstone group reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviewsedward jones reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  revie